{"tid":1325252,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"麥基掛靴無人講？","createTime":"2019-07-16T22:26:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T23:20:16.000Z","uid":30251,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"64c3467db1491305a886a33b1e652928c9058389","tid":1325252,"uid":30251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T22:26:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://sports.now.com/mobileweb/news/details?id=26216224174\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fmobileweb%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D26216224174&d=Xx1rX%2BBWBBKZa4OSQyufSXvcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=5a0af861\" target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/mobileweb/news/details?id=26216224174</a><br />\n【Now Sports-體育】東方龍獅前鋒麥基今午透過球會社交網絡宣佈，在32歲之齡結束近15年職業球員生涯，同時感謝球迷及球會一直以來的支持。<br />\n<br />\n麥基透過東方龍獅Facebook專頁宣佈掛靴的消息，「經過差唔多十年嘅職業足球生涯，我今日決定『掛靴』喇！我好多謝曾經有份合作嘅隊友、教練以及所有職員。讓我擁有過好多美好回憶！同時感謝所有一直支持我同球會嘅粉絲。我祝願東方龍獅未來一切順利～加油！」<br />\n<br />\n在英國伯明翰出生的麥基，10歲時隨家人來港定居，16歲接受正統足球訓練。2005年，17歲的麥基加盟當時在乙組角逐的港會，展開球員生涯，之後先後為傑志、香港飛馬及東方龍獅等效力。2011年12月首為香港代表隊上陣，其間上陣52場入12球，是近年港隊主力前鋒，並領軍奪得2012及2013年省港盃冠軍。<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/4/174/26216224174/26221835181_600x390.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F4%2F174%2F26216224174%2F26221835181_600x390.jpg&h=7c65e424&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca1456fd80779744cc63dc270f39a57d5c8c781c","tid":1325252,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T22:27:14.000Z","msg":"香港足球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6650fc8e7501d1eefbed12223b10b5a74e3e9d7a","tid":1325252,"uid":30251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca1456fd80779744cc63dc270f39a57d5c8c781c","tid":1325252,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T22:27:14.000Z","msg":"香港足球<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T22:30:34.000Z","msg":"仲諗住收工上黎圍爐擺低句「麥基多謝你」就算<br />\n點知竟然無人講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9504854bc72e5eb9c382c1ddc8d0f25b7369f0c","tid":1325252,"uid":34990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T23:20:16.000Z","msg":"香港踢波洋人32歲又算早退wo"}]}